RES osdtriplet
FOB 0
RSI f1 w1 0.0 0.7
! BROKEN: RAYDUMP — legacy code writes integer ray-code fields with a D-format,
! emitting raw NUL/control bytes into the output (not golden-testable as text).
! BROKEN: FOBDUMP — same binary-byte issue as RAYDUMP.
RAYERROR
OPD
CAPFN
FITZERN
LISTZERN
LISTOPD
LISTREPT
CAPGRID 1
WAMAP 1
AMAP 1
IMAGEDIR
